&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://publications.environment-agency.gov.uk/pdf/GEHO0110BRZK-E-e.pdf"&gt;Download form AqHerb01 guidance notes from the Environment Agency website (PDF, 326K)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

