&lt;p&gt;&lt;a rel="external" href="http://customs.hmrc.gov.uk/channelsPortalWebApp/channelsPortalWebApp.portal?_nfpb=true&amp;amp;_pageLabel=pageExcise_ShowContent&amp;amp;id=HMCE_CL_000509&amp;amp;propertyType=document&amp;amp;lang=_e"&gt;Landfill tax guidance on the HMRC website &lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

